history.content:
Want free food and the chance to solve puzzles and win prizes?

Please join us for a Brain Teaser Battle hosted by HKN and Susquehanna International Group! Work with a team to answer as many brainteasers and puzzles as you can in a timed competition to win a prize. Come with your own team of 3-4, or be assigned to a team at the event.
Doordash codes will be provided for participants, as well as prizes for the winners.

This event is open to all UC Berkeley students, no experience necessary.

Details:
When: Tuesday, November 16th at 4:00pm PST
Where: Zoom link will be provided the week of the event
Registration: https://sigsurvey.typeform.com/to/kuuqHqlH
Registration Deadline: November 15th. You do not need a full team to register!
Facebook event: https://fb.me/e/1Z8sCGbl9
